This paper deals with the analysis of Facebook's use of potentially sensitive personal data for advertising purposes, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR) and privacy (cs.CY). The study also involves data mining and machine learning techniques to analyze Facebook's user data, which falls under the categories of social and information retrieval (cs.SI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper discusses potential risks associated with the use of sensitive data, which could fall under the category of system and data security (cs.SD).
